Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you free now?\N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought we could get some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to talk about\Nwhat's been happening
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with you and Mr. Schuwald again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm over that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-But…\N-Sorry. I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a meeting\Nthat my father has to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ther's going to be a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go with…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,DANCE PARTY\N9 P.M., 8TH JUNE 1996
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The library is closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she never has\Nany trouble getting guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something about her…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I seen her somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not really into this kind of thing,\Nbut a friend made me buy tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't go tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dinner with state assembly members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's no ordinary dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure you won't have trouble\Nfinding someone to go with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.\NI didn't really want to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You are researching Margot Langer too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to delete any of it.\NIm researching her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for a paper for a university class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lotte Frank,\Na cultural anthropology major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You are talented, Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about the accountant's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a newspaper article\Non the Voice of God Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are about\Na middle-aged couple's murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was good at investigating,\Nbut you put me to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm investigating unsolved murders\Nthat happened
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,here in Bavaria over the last four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me more\Nof what you know about the murder of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot Langer, the former prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The child born to Margot Langer\Nand Hans Schuwald has been
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized by his father\Nand accepted as his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible his son was involved\Nin the events happening around Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really obsessed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering it's just a paper for class,\Nyou're letting it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just a research paper, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people like you\Never have to worry about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,everything goes your way\Nwhen you're a pretty woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you've never had trouble\Ngetting guys to like you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you ever have\Nthe kind of problems I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Life can be so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come with me to a dance tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't usually come\Nto these kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Give it a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With you around,\Nall the guys will talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See? They're all looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to them.\NI'll be happy with the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, here's one already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Constantine\Nfrom the Supernatural Phenomenon Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. We have attracted a real weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy like you has a lot of nerve\Ntalking to Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you and me\Nhang out together tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in luck, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my type.\NI can't stand his type at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with me, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't think we fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "really!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A ton of guys talked to you,\Nbut you turned them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too picky, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been a while\Nsince I have enjoyed myself like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All these students hanging out,\Nhaving fun, and joking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done this in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, it sounds like…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are pretty straight-laced\Ndespite the way you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? "Despite the way I look"?\NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, baby. Dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He is back! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little dance. Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you are drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not like I think you are hot,\Nyou know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one to talk! That is so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me one dance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then I will get paid.\N-"Paid"? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl asked me\Nto be your date just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So just give me one little dance.\NThat is all I am asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one little song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not do it again! I will not! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because I liked Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped him find his father\Nbecause I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But once he was able to prove\Nthat he was Schuwald's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he has become too busy with his father\Nand does not have any time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All he cares about is his father now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It really hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew that\Ngetting dumped would be so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Life can be so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It will turn out all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad things can't keep happening forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where I can reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I still don't have\Na place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then call me at my place. Promise?\N-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had a good time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find who you are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought… I had seen Nina\Nsomewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks just like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a pretty good shot, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it is the gun\Nthat is doing most of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not have passed the test\Nas an official German Army sniper rifle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but this gun can hit a\Nfive-centimeter target from 300 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with an amateur firing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you are shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but the closer you get to it,\Nthe better your accuracy will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, find a place free of anything\Nthat will block your line of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes with four\N.338 Lapua Magnum rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you will not have time\Nto shoot all four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One shot is all you will ever get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been coming around\Nevery day lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you birdwatching?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We seem to get a lot of visitors\Nin these woods every Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There is that old man\Nand the two young men with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like these woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am making amends to these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been for 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my best dish,\Nbut he hardly touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to win\Nsome fabulous prizes in tonight's quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first contestant\Nis Mr.Weindler from Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what he will win! It is an RV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My family has always wanted one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad, Mr. Weindler.\NCamping in this baby is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll need to answer\Nall ten questions correctly to win it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time for the first question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning on leaving\Nwithout eating a bite again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it last week too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how busy we get,\NI remember all my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have no appetite,\Nthen at least have the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd trip and fall\Nafter years of walking these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just bandaged it to keep it stiff.\NBut get it checked at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw you,\NI thought you were a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gathering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, there was a man\Nwho all the wild birds were friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When he extended his hand like this,\Nthe birds would land on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was a boy, he spent all his time\Nin these woods with the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Hitler came into power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the man joined the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was convinced that the National\NSocialist German Workers' Party
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,would turn the country into\Nthe ideal nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day he was given an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A vicious criminal had escaped\Ninto these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was chosen to go after the criminal\Nsince he knew these woods so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shoot and kill the criminal\Nwhen you find him."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew the woods like\Nthe back of his hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so he tracked the criminal\Nall through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He chased him on and on until…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he cornered the man, he realized\Nhe wasn't a vicious criminal at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but just an ordinary foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet regardless of who the foreigner was,\Nhe had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He carried out the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on,\Nthe birds stopped coming to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For 60 years,\Nhe's been trying to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He would say, "I am sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But the birds never came near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will\Nblood be shed in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
